title: Building instructions landing page - LEGO
snippet: Use the LEGO® Builder app to find instructions The LEGO Builder app is a digital building tool that makes it easier than ever to follow instructions and complete your set. You’ll find hundreds of instructions for both old and new sets that you can use instantly or save. The app makes is simple to search by set number, theme or year. title: LEGO® Play App | Official LEGO® Shop US
snippet: LEGO® Play is the new kid-safe, creative app for all brick lovers, builders and creators! Kids can share their own creations with friends, watch videos, play games or create a LEGO avatar – the adventure starts here!
